<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">12月2日，由广州科技职业技术大学、广东技术师范大学、广州飞瑞敖电子科技股份有限公司主办的全国人工智能职业教育产教融合共同体成立大会在广州隆重举行。江西软件职业技术大学顺利当选全国人工智能职业教育产教融合共同体副理事长单位，并在大会接受授牌。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-12-04%2009%3A54%3A13%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2017014854&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=g88x8tZ2HAlJwcBEEyUnQd90jCw%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">全国人工智能职业教育产教融合共同体将进一步促进人工智能职业教育产业界与教育界的深度合作，通过产学研合作、人才培养、科技成果转化等多种方式，实现各方优势的互补和资源的共享，共同推动创新创业教育和具有工匠精神的高层次技术技能人才的培养，并为各界搭建一个交流合作的平台，为社会经济的可持续发展作出积极贡献。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-12-04%2011%3A36%3A44%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20231204113448.jpg?Expires=2017021004&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=mE%2FqUxm54ZCLINWVIFx6R2QI%2Fnw%3D" alt="" width="650" height="488" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">未来，学校将以此为契机，进一步加强与企业的深度合作，深化产教融合，在专业建设、课程开发、协同育人、师资培养、合作研发、技能比赛等方面发挥各自优势，以培养人工智能技能型人才，推动人工智能技术的发展和应用，为职业教育的繁荣发展作出积极贡献。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>